---
title: Irish Sirloin Steak and Truffle Dauphinoise with pan-fried broccoli
description: Cooked to perfection, melt-in-your-mouth steak is the standout star in this dish. Elevating this meal even further are tender fried broccoli and decadent truffle dauphinoise.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R13_W12_IE_IESB14708-2_Main_high-527f2bd5.jpg
